 	<div id="main-article-info">
 		
					
				
			<h1
																				>Iraq war logs: secret files show how US ignored torture</h1>
				
					<p id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"															>• Massive leak reveals serial detainee abuse <br />• 15,000 unknown civilian deaths in war<br />• <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/iraq-war-logs" title="">Full coverage of the Iraq war logs</a><br />• <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/datablog/2010/oct/23/wikileaks-iraq-data-journalism">Datablog: every death mapped</a></p>
		
				
  	</div>
  	
