 			<div class="section">
				<h1>Iraq war logs: secret files show how US ignored torture</h1>
		   		    			    										This article was published on
							<a href='http://www.guardian.co.uk/'>guardian.co.uk</a>
							at <time datetime="2010-10-23T00:00BST" pubdate>21.26 BST on Friday 22 October 2010</time>. 
					   	A version appeared  on p1 of the <a href=http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2010/oct/23/mainsection  >Main section</a> section of 					   	<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian"  >the Guardian</a>
					   	on <time datetime="2010-10-23" pubdate><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2010/oct/23">Saturday 23 October 2010</a></time>. 
					   	It was last modified at <time datetime="2010-10-26T14:04BST">14.04 BST on Tuesday 26 October 2010</time>.
						  				   								</div>
